creator: Comelit Group S.p.a.
descriptionHtml:
MyComelit is a dynamic and interactive application with numerous personalized services, why should you choose it?
- to simplify and speed up your work
- to configure, manage and monitor all your installed systems from a single app
- to check new promo&offers for you.

What can you do with the MyComelit app?
- Info: you will have direct access to all commercial and technical documentation of our products (catalogs, brochures, manuals, technical data sheets, video tutorials, images and much more).
- Promo: you will easily view all the offers dedicated to you.
- Assistance: wherever you will be, you will have access to our sales and technical contacts in order to ask telephone or field assistance or support for designing a complex system.
- Site management: you will be able to configure and monitor your connected products and systems, to receive reports and alerts from them, directly in the app, via push notifications.

An app designed for you, to offer dedicated services that will help and support you in your everyday work. What are you waiting for? Try it now!

Your feedback is very important to us and that is why we will be glad to receive any advices and suggestions at marketing@comelit.it
